海莉·威廉姆斯透露帕拉摩尔已回到工作室https://www.nme.com/news/music/hayley-williams-reveals-paramore-are-back-in-the-studio-3489968?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=hayley-williams-reveals-paramore-are-回到工作室Will RichardsMon, 28 Aug 2023 20:15:57 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3489968 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="帕拉莫尔" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “扎克·泰勒和我只是想重新开始制作东西。我们已经渴望这一点有一段时间了”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hayley-williams-reveals-paramore-are-back-in-the-studio-3489968">海莉·威廉姆斯 (Hayley Williams) 透露帕拉摩尔 (Paramore) 重返录音室的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="帕拉莫尔" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/ParamoreInterview-00s-emo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hayley-williams">海莉·威廉姆斯</a>透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paramore">帕拉摩尔</a>本周已回到录音室创作新音乐。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/paramore-live-in-new-york-city-review-setlist-photos-3450212">帕拉莫尔 (Paramore) 在纽约市现场演出：仍然处于比赛的顶端</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队最近提前结束了北美巡演， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-cancel-remaining-north-american-tour-dates-due-to-illness-3481115">由于威廉姆斯的肺部感染，最后的演出被取消</a>。威廉姆斯在德克萨斯州休斯顿的一场演出中生病后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paramore-postpone-san-francisco-show-sickness-3472273">乐队推迟了四场现场演出</a>，并提前结束了巡演。</p><p>现在，乐队在 Instagram 上分享了工作室照片，威廉姆斯在 Discord 上确认他们确实正在创作新音乐。</p><p> “我们已经离开公路好几个星期了……主要是在洛杉矶。值得庆幸的是，我们有一些休息时间，但我们也投入了一些工作，”她告诉粉丝。 “回到工作室感觉很好。一旦我们回到纳什维尔，就会有更多这样的事情。”</p><p>威廉姆斯继续说道：“扎克·泰勒和我只想重新开始创作。我们渴望这一点已经有一段时间了。不仅是创作过程，还有创作过程中可能出现的隔离层。”</p><p>谈到她的病情，威廉姆斯补充道：“我简直不敢相信我不再日夜咳嗽了。我的胃仍然受到 10 种药物的折磨……我很高兴能多休息。</p><p> “现在我们今年的大部分巡演已经结束，我希望能够一头扎进创造一些更好的惯例。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cwd9GDTpL9r/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bott