露皮塔·尼永奥 (Lupita Nyong'o) 纪念查德威克·博斯曼 (Chadwick Boseman) 逝世三周年https://www.nme.com/news/film/lupita-nyongo-tribute-chadwick-boseman-third-anniversary-death-3489966?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lupita-nyongo-tribute-chadwick-boseman-third-周年纪念日Will RichardsMon, 28 Aug 2023 19:28:51 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3489966 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="露皮塔·尼永奥和查德维克·博斯曼" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这种困惑是如此深刻，以至于花了几个月的时间才再次相信快乐的感觉”</p><p>露皮塔<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/lupita-nyongo-tribute-chadwick-boseman-third-anniversary-death-3489966">·尼永奥 (Lupita Nyong&#39;o) 在查德维克·博斯曼 (Chadwick Boseman) 逝世三周年之际向他致敬的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="露皮塔·尼永奥和查德维克·博斯曼" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/lupita-nyongo-chadwick-boseman-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lupita-nyong-o">露皮塔·尼永奥</a>在<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/black-panther">《黑豹》</a></em>联合主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chadwick-boseman">查德维克·博斯曼</a>去世三周年之际向他致敬。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/chadwick-boseman-obituary-real-life-superhero-2740722">查德维克·博斯曼 – 1976-2020：现实生活中的超级英雄，给许多人带来了希望</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/black-panther-star-chadwick-boseman-dies-after-four-year-cancer-battle-2740493">博斯曼于 2020 年 8 月 28 日因结肠癌去世，</a>享年 43 岁，粉丝和明星纷纷悼念。</p><p>她在 Instagram 上分享了一张博斯曼在机场的黑白照片，她写道：“三年前的今天，听到查德维克·博斯曼去世的消息，我经历了一种奇异的痛苦。这种困惑如此深刻，以至于花了几个月的时间才再次相信喜悦的感觉。</p><p> “这是我 2018 年抵达韩国时在机场拍摄的照片。我们刚刚学会用手指做婴儿心脏。查德威克在这里增添了他温文尔雅的光芒。我们在那里度过了愉快的 72 个小时，回忆让我充满了快乐。”</p><p>她补充道：“死亡很难理解，甚至更难接受。但他的生活所产生的爱将为他缺席的每个周年纪念日提供动力。</p><p> “查德威克可能不再出现在我们的照片中，但他将永远在我们心中。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CwfnGTwriS4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" backgr